{"type":"answer","id":44627,"parentType":"question","parentId":10294,"uid":6966,"contents":"据说有，但是似乎并没说清怎么领。领的话似乎还要审核，条件比较苛刻的那种。<br>\n因此我最喜欢的一家日料店最近危了，似乎真的半年没开门了。前些年开业的时候经济就低迷，但是还能基本座满，这段时间店面不开门，只有外送了。<br>\n不过大公司似乎是有减税降费等等补助，毕竟大而不倒，老美帝了。<br>\n事业机关（基层）单位似乎更惨，根本就是不补了睡大觉。<br>\n对岸民国这种补助根本不存在的。<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/kFSVcCU.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/kFSVcCU.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/kFSVcCU.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/WhtYLCx.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/WhtYLCx.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/WhtYLCx.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-06-27","agreeCount":1,"discussionCount":1}